reviewText: I was very impressed with this DVD. It is the best makeup artistry DVD I have seen! I have ordered many makeup DVD's on Amazon before and there have been some good ones and some not so good ones out there. I highly recommend this DVD if you are serious about improving you makeup artistry skills. This DVD is so good its even better than some classes I have attended. This DVD delivers step by step instruction, I guarantee you will learn something new.

Ask yourself, what sets me a part as a makeup artist? If you're not sure, purchase this DVD and you will learn how to become diverse and use tools you never imagined possible for makeup artistry. This DVD sets the pros and the amateurs a part. Which one do you want to be? Get this DVD and learn how to become an artist.
